Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for sale 50 Bennett Street, East Perth.

The property comprises 110sqm* of building area situated on an irregular shaped land parcel of 230sqm*, located on the doorstep to the Perth CBD and within walking distance to East Perth’s prestigious Waterfront dining precinct.

Zoned ‘Town Centre’ under the City of Perth’s CPS No. 2, permitted uses include retail, dining and business services.

The property is offered with a medium-term leaseback via offers to purchase invited, closing Wednesday 9th October 2019 at 4pm.

For further details or to request the information memorandum, please contact the exclusive selling agents CBRE.

This 450sqm office premises presents to a high standard and is fully cabled and partitioned into executive offices, open plan workstations, boardroom, meeting rooms and a training room.

Located at the Eastern end of the Perth CBD on the corner of Adelaide Terrace and Plain Street, within the Hyatt Hotel complex.

Lease Type: Assignment of Lease expiring 1 October 2009
Lease Options: 1 year + 1 year options
Outgoings: Estimated at $124.56/sqm per annum
Parking: Undercover secure basement car bays available direct through Wilson's Parking at a rate of $327.58 per bay per calendar month

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact Kendall Forrest on 0439 700 717 or kendall.forrest@cbre.com.au
